emailNotification.emailBody:
Please sign the following release, which is necessary for your child to participate in MITOC activities.

To complete this waiver process, please call the MITOC desk at (302) 648-6246, and leave a voice message confirming that you've executed a release waiver. Please include your name & the name of your child in the voice message.
